{
  "stem": "11272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of course, they-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they must have been miserable people at home, because they certainly got their pleasures out of making our lives miserable.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not only was I not able to get any information about my family, I-- I didn't-- [SIGHS]-- I didn't know whether I was alive.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But finally, about the third or fourth month I was there, as I was being marched from the appellplatz, from the main section, to watch as they were hanging some people-- they put up hanging parades-- I looked over, and I saw my brother Sam.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in the same camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were not allowed to get together, but we somehow or other managed to see each other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did everything possible to at least see each other once a week.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but I was able to throw him a kiss or wave at him and sometimes say [NON-ENGLISH], how are you?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it wasn't too often that we got the chance, because he was way in the other end of the camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all we did is encourage each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] please stay alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Are you OK?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Are you all right?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, one time a truck of-- a full truck with tomatoes was passing the road, and then it a little bump, and some tomatoes fell over.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, we dove for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I picked up five little, teeny tomatoes, green tomatoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I carried them inside my jacket for about three or four days till I found my brother Sam to give it to him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because I didn't eat tomatoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We did a lot of those kind of things.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
